# SPARE-PIM VOC trace examples.
# Format: VOC voc0,voc1,... [addr] [mac_cmds] [acc_cmds]
#
# Token 0: all VOCs are zero, so sparse ACT-SPM-PRE is skipped.
VOC 0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0 0x0

# Token 1: max_voc=3, total_voc=8. SPM stays within one ESDM V row.
VOC 1,3,2,0,1,0,0,1 0x40

# Token 2: max_voc=6. With esdm_columns_per_row=4 this splits into two SPM rows.
VOC 6,1,0,0,0,0,0,0 0x80
